  "description": "\u00c2\u00a9 Copyright 2008 Blue Cross and Blue Shield of Kansas City\n\nCalled by:\n                    \n\nPROCESSING : Reads data from the SavRx Claim file and creats a common output\n\nModifications:                        \n Developer                      Date               Project/Altiris #        Change Description                                                                  Development Project       Code Reviewer            Date Reviewed\n-----------------------------------    -------------------    ---------------------------     ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------    ----------------------------------      -------------------------           -------------------------   \nKaushik Kapoor              2018-03-30     5828                        Initial Programming                                                                    EnterpriseDev2                Kalyan Neelam            2018-04-20\nKaushik Kapoor              2018-09-10     5828                        Changed the logic of calculation of PRCS_DT and added       EnterpriseDev2                Hugh Sisson               2018-09-19\n                                                                                              1753-01 incase no date found\n\nAnnotations:\nThis job extracts data from SavRx claims file and load file date and other required details in to a common layout for further use."
